pr_body:
**Project Update** 
Date : September 12th , 2022
The new PassManager is now functional in Enzyme besides the legacy PassManager .  So enzyme can now be used with both the pass managers. Tests (.ll files) remain to be updated so that they would also test Enzyme for the new pass manager.


**---------------------------------------------------------**
Date : April 17th , 2022
I am  applying for GSoC'22 Enzyme New pass manager integration project. This pull request is to present my candidacy. Any suggestion would be greatly helpful.


fixes #584
